sub_title: Head of Discipline Supportability Engineering & Manager Customer Training at Thales Netherlands
summary:
Head of Discipline Supportability Engineering, responsible for competencies and processes for the Supportability disciplines Logistics Engineering & Obsolescence,  Customer Documentation and Customer Training 

Manager of Thales Netherlands' Customer Training team. Responsible for management of the team of 15+ technical trainers, 1 E-learning Developer and 1 Welfare Officer.

The training is focused on the operation and maintenance of Thales Netherlands' Combat Management System (TACTICOS), and radars.
